      <header>About</header>
      <p>
        This website is the final project for ITIS 4166. The purpose of this
        website is to create a login/logout and registration system with
        authentication that is all connected to a database. After logging in,
        the user will enter their budget data and it will generate three
        different charts that display the data in a readable way. The user can
        save all their budget data to their account and view it when they log
        back in sometime in the future.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

