    <div class="col-sm-12">
      <header>Project details</header>
      <p>
        This project uses NodeJS on the backend and a web template called EJS
        for the frontend. Bootstrap is the frontend framework used in designing
        the navigation menu and all the page layouts. MongoDB is used as the
        database and MongoDB Atlas is a cloud database service used to manage
        the data. ChartJS is the library used to display the budget data in the
        three different charts on the dashboard page.
      </p>
